'''East Coast Barbarians''' is a Norwegian [[Rugby union|rugby]] team. They currently compete in the [[Norway Rugby Championship]]. The team is not a club as such, as it contains players from different clubs that have too low player numbers to compete individually. The club contains players from Tønsberg, Horten, Høyskolen i Vestfold and NMBU (Ås). 

