{{seealso|Chinese Cycling Association}}
[[Image:Hkca.png|thumb|right|HKCA logo]]
The '''Hong Kong Cycling Association''' (in [[Traditional Chinese]]: 香港單車聯會) or '''HKCA''' is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Hong Kong]].

It is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Asian Cycling Confederation]].

